name: Chili truck
description:
Chili truck is a truck that loads chili, garlic, onion, and various kinds of vegetables up to 10 to 14 tons in weight at a high speed of 100 - 160 km/hour on the highway. Even though the job of being a chili truck driver has a high risk of death and their salary is low, they are willing to work to deliver various kinds of crops so that they don't rot on the road and the farmers make a profit.

keep the spirit of truck driver friends, your services bring ekonomi prosperity.
